<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/public-prosecution-service-for-northern-ireland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The PPS is the principal prosecuting authority in Northern Ireland. In addition to taking decisions as to prosecution in cases investigated by the police in Northern Ireland, it also considers cases investigated by other statutory authorities, such as HM Revenue and Customs. PPSNI works with the Northern Ireland Executive ."@en .
